44 EulerVector ToEulerAngles(Quaternion q) {
45  EulerVector angles;
46 
47  // roll (x-axis rotation)
48  double sinr_cosp = 2 * (q.w * q.x + q.y * q.z);
49  double cosr_cosp = 1 - 2 * (q.x * q.x + q.y * q.y);
50  double roll = std::atan2(sinr_cosp, cosr_cosp);
51 
52  // pitch (y-axis rotation)
53  double sinp = std::sqrt(1 + 2 * (q.w * q.y - q.x * q.z));
54  double cosp = std::sqrt(1 - 2 * (q.w * q.y - q.x * q.z));
55  double pitch = 2 * std::atan2(sinp, cosp) - M_PI / 2;
56 
57  // yaw (z-axis rotation)
58  double siny_cosp = 2 * (q.w * q.z + q.x * q.y);
59  double cosy_cosp = 1 - 2 * (q.y * q.y + q.z * q.z);
60  double yaw = std::atan2(siny_cosp, cosy_cosp);
61 
62 
63  angles << roll,pitch,yaw;
64  return angles;
65 }
